                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     Veerappan wife
                            
	Chennai, Nov. 26: The widow of slain forest brigand Veerappan was arrested today with three others from Tamil Nadus Mettur in connection with three murder cases dating back to the early 90s. One of the three, Ponnusamy, is Veerappans cousin.                                                                                                                                                                                  
